attributes.title: Awaken your multiple life energies and master your destiny!
attributes.description:
Satsang summary: 

Your whole biology thinks. If you understand this one truth, you can master all the life energies in you. If you master your life energies, you will master your destiny. Mastering your life energy is the fundamental principle for any success. Without mastering the life energy, any success you taste or think you tasted, is accidental or unknowingly mastering one or two life energies. All the life energies put together is Parashakti. Be in Oneness with Parashakti and let Parashakti manifest in all of us and awaken all the life energies in us.

Satsang delivered on October 5 2019
